Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.86,0:02:03.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.67,0:02:16.81,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:22.32,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you plan to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:24.58,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will join up with Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:27.56,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Scythe betrayed the organization and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.85,0:02:30.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He abandoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:40.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The situation is still unclear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.75,0:02:44.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will join up with Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:47.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If joining him is impossible, I will aid in his escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:51.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I distract them, I can draw off some of his pursuers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:53.72,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pull over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:54.94,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:59.24,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}While the hunt is still in progress, you need to stay with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.11,0:03:05.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Scythe is under the protection of Phantom even as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:09.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The fear of Phantom is always with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:12.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's the reason the organization can't make careless moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:16.25,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you were to be captured here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:18.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Scythe would be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:21.96,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You've changed, Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:23.72,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:24.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:27.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You are a different person from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:30.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.98,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're no longer "Zwei".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:35.65,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're Azuma Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:36.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You were listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:39.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have a place to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:41.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There is a real you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:43.20,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:47.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...I have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:49.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:52.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A number.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.71,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Master is the only place I have to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:57.72,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.75,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:03.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Master gave me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:07.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...a name, Ein, and nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:08.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.32,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.42,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:17.73,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Phan...tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:19.74,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:31.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:32.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:21.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:26.79,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You didn't think I'd be gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.61,0:05:31.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're reckless, but you're not a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:48.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The stolen van has been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:50.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So we let them all escape, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:01.62,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Scythe is your pet dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:03.08,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take care of this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:07.10,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm fully aware of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:19.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know this song?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:21.96,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Was it too loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:23.56,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is its name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:27.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't know... I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:30.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I forgot the title, but I heard it pretty often in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:33.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Does everyone in Japan listen to this kind of music?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everyone has their own preferences when it comes to music.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:38.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no difference there between Japan and Las Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:41.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tell me about Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You remembered, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:48.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Memories of when you were living your life as Azuma Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:51.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:17.84,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:19.95,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The cargo is on schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.25,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wish you a safe trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:23.48,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:26.27,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The escape and transport route,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:29.25,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}you took care of it down to every little detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.80,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll contact you again after things have settled down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:37.31,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hope we will be on good terms in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.56,0:07:42.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She can't be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:45.41,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we get careless, she will sell out the whole Godou clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:46.93,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:51.03,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We've been using her as well, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.36,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:56.47,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't chicken out now, Shiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:57.88,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Make up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:02.52,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm gonna be big. {cj: gonna -> going to? would like to give him a coarse way of speaking, but can't decide on whether I want to leave "gonna" in}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:18.03,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Azuma Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.98,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You should go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.16,0:08:25.04,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:25.92,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:27.88,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where would I go back to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:31.61,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You should know what I've done in the past half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.47,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't go back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:36.21,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have a past, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.21,0:08:39.43,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can exist in this world as Azuma Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:41.18,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're no different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:41.91,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:46.32,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have something I don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:48.12,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There is something to prove your identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:56.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is something like this important?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:04.44,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes. That's your proof of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:05.64,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's something I don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:17.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.10,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.88,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you realize what you've done?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:28.76,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That was your...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:29.98,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was just a piece of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:35.03,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My memories make me who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:36.50,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And you have those too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:42.57,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You told me about your dreams before, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.57,0:09:43.35,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Memories of colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:46.75,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They are bright and dazzling with a strong wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:50.21,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Those are memories of your homeland, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:52.21,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They are fleeting memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:53.77,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no guarantee that it's my homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:56.46,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But it's your memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:58.66,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have a past too-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:01.03,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}not as a number like "Ein".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.04,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have a real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:06.14,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why? Why are you so concerned about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:07.26,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have nothing to gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:10.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:12.33,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want them to slaughter you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:13.86,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not for anyone's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:15.29,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is my own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.88,0:10:20.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Doing this is my proof of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:24.51,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't need a stamp on paper for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:26.51,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}None of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.33,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your driving license, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:43.69,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:44.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Las Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:46.33,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We were visiting a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:48.81,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wallace Young, 20 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:50.47,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You look younger in the flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.47,0:10:52.35,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hear that quite often.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:53.37,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And your company?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:53.88,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:56.87,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She doesn't look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:01.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, it's a long journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:02.43,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's a bit carsick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:03.31,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:06.14,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay, drive on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:12.64,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You've become smoother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:15.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hmm? The act just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:18.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you saying? You taught me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:39.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What will you do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:44.70,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We'll keep on moving and stop from time to time to let you rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:48.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And when your wounds have healed, let's go someplace faraway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.78,0:11:50.25,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Faraway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:50.68,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:52.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:55.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:57.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:00.14,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I decided this of my own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:05.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll buy something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:33.53,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein! Ein!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:24.02,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I felt no fear yesterday, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:26.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...my finger...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:28.54,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:30.91,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.55,0:13:32.95,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:33.87,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Put me at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:38.83,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're too selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:39.63,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong, Ein?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:45.83,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You used to be much stronger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:49.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:50.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:53.10,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...was only doing it for Master's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:55.59,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just for that reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:59.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if it meant making the whole organization my enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.85,0:14:01.60,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}if Master commanded it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:04.08,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:06.56,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.63,0:14:09.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...living for what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:13.46,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Chased by the organization and just running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:15.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't even pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:19.75,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I had died yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:22.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...at least I could have died as Ein.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.72,0:14:24.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:27.94,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Were we fighting this whole time just to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:32.77,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:34.97,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We fought to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:37.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We didn't want to die for a stupid reason like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:45.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We wanted to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:50.46,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That... is the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:02.65,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm being chased by Inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:05.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If our pursuers found this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:10.31,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The organization or me, who would you point your gun at?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:13.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't need to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:14.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll point it at the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:17.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll pull the trigger of my own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:20.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:22.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you trying to survive so desperately?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:30.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you telling me to live the same life?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.35,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't you want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.35,0:15:34.08,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.08,0:15:35.79,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm no one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:37.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:41.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Neither a reason to live nor a role.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:44.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ein...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:47.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:48.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's stop calling you "Ein".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:51.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Ein" is just a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:51.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's not a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:55.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You need a new name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:57.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:15:59.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not like Phantom or a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:03.44,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A name for you to live your life by.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:07.63,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:08.80,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:12.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going to call you Elen from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:16.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why "Elen"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:18.63,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't need a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:19.58,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.94,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not as an assassin or a puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.43,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a name for you to keep on living as yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:27.60,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:31.42,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:32.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a bit strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:33.82,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen, let's look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:38.59,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The past you've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:02.15,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Once we've found your real name,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:05.12,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}there will be plenty of reasons to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.78,0:17:10.14,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if you have to hurt someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.14,0:17:12.88,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}keep on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:15.83,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We might suffer for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:17.15,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:18.14,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:30.67,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If that boy you like joins Scythe's side...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.51,0:17:32.16,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...what should be done?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:35.95,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.19,0:17:49.10,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going to withdraw some money and get a new car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:50.52,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will be back in an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:52.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How's your wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.69,0:17:54.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be fine if I don't force myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:02.22,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Be careful, Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:04.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Alright,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:05.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:20.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:23.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The name Reiji gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:27.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}With this name, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:03.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How unlike you, Ein...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:08.55,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Overcome your pain with willpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:12.25,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:26.68,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Last exit, Zwei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:28.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Has your sweet honeymoon been fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:30.67,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lizzie...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.35,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Looks like you've been played by Scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:39.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have no business with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:40.69,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.69,0:19:43.56,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We shall have a long conversation about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:46.06,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just got an update.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:49.46,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My subordinate tailing Phantom has been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:51.76,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Phantom has returned to Scythe's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:55.13,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.82,0:19:58.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:00.62,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Spill it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.16,0:20:03.45,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where's Scythe headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.14,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know. We were just...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:16.22,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As I thought, he knows nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:18.54,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:19.87,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:29.28,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll acknowledge that stubbornness of yours, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.85,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I've killed the microphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:37.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can tell me anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.69,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Saving Ein and running together...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Was that your choice?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:51.16,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:53.81,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They branded you an accomplice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}People question your loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.63,0:20:58.89,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your chance to return to Japan is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:03.09,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:06.95,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...there is one last option open to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:10.67,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A way to prove your innocence,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:12.82,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...and take Ein back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:17.21,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What... is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:40.89,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You should know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:42.23,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...how to use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:21:58.49,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will kill Scythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.51,0:23:36.22,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:39.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll make you smile someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.26,0:23:40.39,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll return to you a normal smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.39,0:23:43.57,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll return to you a normal smile.
